Interface TupleIterator

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterator<List<Member>>, TupleCursor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractTupleIterator, AbstractTupleList.AbstractTupleListIterator

    public interface TupleIterator
extends Iterator<List<Member>>, TupleCursor
    Extension to Iterator that returns tuples.

    Extends TupleCursor to support the standard Java iterator API. For some implementations, using the iterator API (in particular the Iterator.next() and Iterator.hasNext() methods) may be more expensive than using cursor's TupleCursor.forward() method.

    Author:
    jhyde
